We started with a gorgeous London Lobster Salad, a modern British delight with avocado, corn, tomatoes, and a zesty grapefruit vinaigrette. The New York stuffed Alaskan King Crab, bold and innovative with uni crema and smoked roe, reflecting NYCâ€™s culinary creativity.  Both were light and great starts before the steaks.

The Margaret River 7oz Australian Wagyu Bottom Skirt @margaretriver_wagyubeef  was next, with the Masami Ranch 12 oz American Wagyu New York Strip @masamiranch.  We loved both of these steaks.

We finished the meal with this dessert platter board that included a sampling of their desserts, including their special "sweet and spicy" key lime pie that comes with a strawberry habanero sauce.

